Step into the mysterious sands of Dune! This Chrome extension brings the legendary atmosphere of Arrakis to your new tab every time you open it.

The Dune live wallpaper extension captures the awe-inspiring beauty and danger of the desert planet. With a sleek design, it combines breathtaking visuals with essential tools, enhancing your browsing with both style and functionality.

Navigate smoothly with a Google search bar, customizable shortcuts to favorite sites, and a clock-date display to stay organized and informed.

Key Features:
Live Wallpaper inspired by the world of Dune
Google Search Bar for easy browsing
Customizable site shortcuts for quick access
Clock-Date display for real-time updates

Explore the world of Dune every time you open a new tab! Discover more unique themes at Gameograf.com to personalize your browser experience.
